AWS SNS Security Alert Integration
Integrated Amazon SNS (Simple Notification Service) with the AWS Security Compliance Monitoring solution.
Configured automated email notifications for critical security findings detected across AWS infrastructure.
Developed AWS Lambda functions to analyze EC2 Security Groups, identify exposed ports (SSH, RDP, Database Ports), and publish alerts to SNS topics.
Implemented real-time notifications for:
Publicly exposed SSH (Port 22)
Publicly exposed RDP (Port 3389)
Publicly accessible database ports (MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, etc.)
Non-compliant Security Group configurations
Generated detailed compliance reports including:
Instance Name
Instance ID
Public IP
Open Port
Risk Level (Critical/High/Medium)
Recommended Remediation
Used SNS Topic:
arn:aws:sns:ap-south-1:152031363284:security-compliance-alerts
Reduced manual security audits by enabling automated compliance monitoring and instant alerting.


